{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2854 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2854 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2854","linkify":"Compiler Error C2854","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2854","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"syntax error in #pragma hdrstop","pos":[618,649]},{"content":"The <ph id=\"ph1\">`#pragma hdrstop`</ph> gives an invalid filename.","pos":[656,704],"source":"The `#pragma hdrstop` gives an invalid filename."},{"content":"The pragma can be followed by an optional filename in parentheses and quotation marks:","pos":[705,791]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2854:","pos":[798,835]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2854 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2854\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2854\"\nms.assetid: 917fec9c-790a-4149-8dfc-00d17a09199c\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2854\nsyntax error in #pragma hdrstop  \n  \n The `#pragma hdrstop` gives an invalid filename. The pragma can be followed by an optional filename in parentheses and quotation marks:  \n  \n The following sample generates C2854:  \n  \n```  \n// C2854.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \n#pragma hdrstop( \"\\\\source\\\\pchfiles\\\\myheader.pch\" ]   // C2854  \n// try the following line instead  \n// #pragma hdrstop( \"\\\\source\\\\pchfiles\\\\myheader.pch\" )  \n```"}